{
  "stem": "18626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working in-- in the [GERMAN] in the workshops in the ghetto until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the last actually day when they start to take us to that gate to transport to Germany.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a lot of experiences while I was working in the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I recall, in 1941 when the [GERMAN], I think it was around December [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before Christmas, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] a-- the German commandant from the [GERMAN] and the ghetto-- Commandant Wiedmann was his name.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wiedmann.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "W-I-E-D-M-A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was the commandant, and taking care and checking out how the workshops work, and now everybody's manufacturing things, and how all the work is going on, and if everything goes through.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Used to come all the time and check out how all the workers are working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was very happy all the time, seeing that the leather coats by the tailors are coming out excellent, and the leather boots are the most beautiful work he ever seen.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the German uniforms are made excellent to order for the big gestapo people and the other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the toy factory is doing a golden job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, one of his friends [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] who had vacation from the Russian front, one of his comrades, he invited to show off.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the big leader with that swastika, you know, carrying on with the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was showing off his friend all the job it's doing with the Juden, with the Jews, and with the work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he took him on a tour, that German, his friend who came for vacation from front, from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they start walking him to the workshops.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
